data.title: Expressions of Color and Light: Exhibit and Sale of John Richardson Watercolors
data.meta_description: This is an exhibit and sale of watercolor paintings by Tennessee artist John F. Richardson.  Sale of artwork will benefit the Mack S. Prichard Foundation for Tennessee parks and conservation. The show is at the Cummins Falls State Park Visitor Center.
